HEADWORD: Pardoning
<hw>Par"don*ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Relating to pardon; having or
exercising the right to pardon; willing to pardon; merciful; <as>as, the
<ex>pardoning</ex> power; a <ex>pardoning</ex> God.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

